{"tid":746653,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人一掂到污糟嘢就會敏感","createTime":"2018-07-17T17:05:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-17T17:30:30.000Z","uid":109975,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"243ce0803cb84af3f089bd6cfc699fa71922b3d6","tid":746653,"uid":109975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T17:05:11.000Z","msg":"呢排搬屋要執嘢<br />\n發現自己一執啲污糟同多塵嘅嘢<br />\n隻手/腳就會敏感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一條條好似蚊咬咁<br />\n但係洗完手 半個鐘之後又會無哂事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過而家就算唔執嘢 每日一出街坐巴士都會敏感<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢張係有次搣完荔枝就起咗呢啲一條條<br />\n唔知係咪污糟定有農藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/005304_86d68224ea7802dd4266e0875d6a78bb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F005304_86d68224ea7802dd4266e0875d6a78bb.png&h=88cd487e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有無人可以話比我聽呢啲係咩嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21569ec49309b262c814805712dc8818ea7f59ec","tid":746653,"uid":43518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T17:13:21.000Z","msg":"劃痕性蕁麻疹"},{"pid":"5054abefef5824e8308e84edbb1fe88c9c8e324a","tid":746653,"uid":109975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21569ec49309b262c814805712dc8818ea7f59ec","tid":746653,"uid":43518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T17:13:21.000Z","msg":"劃痕性蕁麻疹"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T17:30:30.000Z","msg":"啱啱google咗 好似真係有啲似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔該哂巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}